creator: Better way
descriptionHtml:
A Wordle puzzle game is a daily word puzzle game! The Wordle puzzle game is in your pocket now. Come back every hour for a new Word.
<========Rules========>
Guess the correct word in 6 tries.
Each guess must be a valid 5 letter word.
After each guess, the color of the tiles will change to show how close your guess was to the word.
Color = grey =>Letter is not in the word in any spot.
Color = orange => Letter is in the word but at a different spot.
Color == green =>Letter is in the word and at the correct spot.

Game Features

1. Fun Word Puzzles
Play the viral word game, or try one of our fun and creative game modes for a unique challenge like you’ve never seen before

2. Play at Your Own Pace:
Whether you enjoy the pressure of a timed challenge or want to try to go the duration in Secret Word mode. Wordle! Has several games to play at your desired pace

3. Relax with Wordle!
Is life getting a little crazy? Why not take a load off and relax with these fun word puzzles?

4. Flex Your Brain Muscles
Ready for a tougher challenge? Test your skills in more challenging levels with longer words! Will you be the Wordle! Champion?

Wordler is the daily word puzzle game! Wordler is in your pocket now. Come back every day for a new challenge, or play custom puzzles as many times as you'd like

Guess a word and use the tile colors to help guide your next decision. You get 6 tries to guess the correct word

If you enjoy Scrabble, crosswords, or just about any word game, you will enjoy Wordle

Also includes custom puzzles so you can try wordler with more than 5 letters

More content coming in each update

<========Rules========>
